&lt;li&gt;In collaboration with internal stakeholders, ensure risk-based quality management is applied as appropriate to specific studies (e.g. through helping to facilitate the identification of critical data and critical data processes, and risks associated with them, establishing, monitoring and reporting out on Quality Tolerance Limits (QTLS))&lt;/li&gt;
