&lt;li&gt;Lead and manage cross-functional submission team meetings and workstreams (Regulatory, Clinical, Quality, CMC, Medical Writing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee project team delivery of the marketing authorization applications&lt;/li&gt;
