&lt;li&gt;Advanced proficiency working with critical clinical trial technologies, specifically Electronic Data Capture (EDC), IRT, and eCOA dashboard environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to synthesize complex operational metrics and patient data trends into immediate, actionable risk-mitigation workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional interpersonal and relationship-management skills, with a track record of successfully navigating high-stakes conversations with PIs, coordinators, and external vendors&lt;/li&gt;
